        <mxCell id="cost-note" value="MVP 예상 비용 (factory-a 단독):&#10;1번 VPC 고정 ~$0.50/월 (Route53 hosted zone)&#10;사용량 ~$1.34/월 (CloudFront + API GW + Lambda + DDB + S3)&#10;합계 ~$1.84/월&#10;※ NAT GW 제거(ADR 0011)로 ~$45/월 절감" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fillColor=#FFF8E1;strokeColor=#F9A825;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="800" y="700" width="380" height="100" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

        <mxCell id="adr-ref" value="결정 근거 (docs/changes/):&#10;0005  워크스트림 A/B 분리&#10;0006  Frontend = Vite 정적 SPA + S3/CloudFront&#10;0007  Dashboard API = Lambda + API Gateway, Lambda는 VPC 밖&#10;0008  Cognito (Self sign-up Disabled, MFA Required)&#10;0009  S3 단일 bucket aegis-bucket-data + raw/processed prefix&#10;0010  Gabia 신규 도메인 + Route53 위임 (Admin UI 도메인과 분리)&#10;0011  1번 VPC NAT Gateway 제거 (MVP)" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=10;fillColor=#FAFAFA;strokeColor=#616161;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1200" y="700" width="500" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>

